    <item>
      <title>软银集团旗下 PayPay Securities 计划实现账户数翻番</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/softbank-group-firm-paypay-securities-aims-to-double-accounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PayPay Securities Corp. 首席执行官表示，该公司计划在本财年结束前（截至 3 月份）将其经纪账户数量从现在的 100 万个增加一倍至 200 万个，这得益于该集团无现金支付系统用户的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/softbank-group-firm-paypay-securities-aims-to-double-accounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 01:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
